
Design Pattern Defination:


Categorization of design pattern
---------------------------------
     1-> Creational Design pattern
                 a> Factory
                 b> Builder
                 c> Singleton

     2-> Structural Design pattern
                 a> Proxy
                 b> Adaptor

     3-> Behavioral Design pattern
                 a> Observer
                 b> State
                 c> Iterator
Singleton Design Pattern
--------------------------
Used for creating object only once and can be reused again and again .




Abstract Design Pattern : This is also used for object creation but this design pattern just has one more layer, which adds one more layer for object creation.

Builder Design Pattern : It is used to create object one by one